short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays all active tabs as a grid overlay

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: "Keyboarder" is a unique Chrome extension designed to revolutionize the way users navigate through their active tabs. Built for those who constantly juggle multiple tabs and seek a more efficient method of tab management, Keyboarder transforms the conventional tab-switching experience into a sleek, keyboard-centric process.
